1 ctrFun(M)      1000000   5.387  1.00541      5.35     0.01          0         0
R> microbenchmark(ctrFun(M), cpyFun(M), times=1e6)
Unit: nanoseconds
       expr  min   lq median   uq      max
1 cpyFun(M) 1211 1314   1358 1426 49533807
2 ctrFun(M) 1202 1301   1346 1415 49842042
