From edd at debian.org  Tue Oct 25 14:48:13 2011
From: edd at debian.org (Dirk Eddelbuettel)
Date: Tue, 25 Oct 2011 07:48:13 -0500
Subject: [Rcpp-devel] What are RcppExport, BEGIN_RCPP and END_RCPP?
In-Reply-To: <CANYYcsLOUEFNGQCHy=uCzdpnvoDy3FenxvuDwx2xV2D1AmuK4A@mail.gmail.com>
